So you can swim...

542
01:00:23,562 --> 01:00:25,029
...and dance and...

543
01:00:26,098 --> 01:00:27,258
...play!

544
01:00:37,576 --> 01:00:39,510
You! All of you!

545
01:00:40,445 --> 01:00:42,037
I'm going back to my own time!

546
01:00:42,280 --> 01:00:44,714
I won't bother to tell
of the useless struggle...

547
01:00:44,783 --> 01:00:46,307
...the hopeless future.

548
01:00:46,418 --> 01:00:48,386
But at least I could die among men!

549
01:04:09,521 --> 01:04:10,681
What are you doing?

550
