No, you mustn't.

564
01:04:54,432 --> 01:04:56,229
Help me gather some wood.

565
01:05:11,549 --> 01:05:12,982
That's a girl.

566
01:05:22,027 --> 01:05:23,119
Where are you from?

567
01:05:26,131 --> 01:05:28,599
As a matter of fact, I'm from right here.

568
01:05:31,436 --> 01:05:33,802
That's where my house used to be...

569
01:05:34,739 --> 01:05:36,673
...many thousands of years ago.

570
01:05:38,943 --> 01:05:40,035
You see there?

571
01:05:42,313 --> 01:05:45,043
From there up to those panels
was my laboratory.

572
01:05:46,151 --> 01:05:49,120
Beyond the panels
was where my garden used to be.

573
01:05:51,856 --> 01:05:52,845
Right there.

574
01:05:54,025 --> 01:05:55,788
That was my library.

575
01:05:56,928 --> 01:06:00,955
Where I once sat talking with friends
about the time machine.

576
01:06:12,444 --> 01:06:13,877
You know, Weena...

577
01:06:15,447 --> 01:06:17,312
...I'd hoped to learn a great deal.

578
01:06:20,919 --> 01:06:24,980
I'd hoped to take back the knowledge
and the advancement mankind had made.

579
01:06:26,291 --> 01:06:28,282
Instead, I find vegetables.

580
01:06:29,761 --> 01:06:32,559
The human race reduced
to living vegetables.

581
01:06:45,543 --> 01:06:46,771
They're gone.

582
01:06:47,112 --> 01:06:48,477
Are you all right?

583
01:06:52,617 --> 01:06:54,642
- That was a Morlock, was it?
- Yes.

584
