Don't you worry.
The fire seems to keep them away.

585
01:07:12,704 --> 01:07:14,262
What are you doing?

586
01:07:14,439 --> 01:07:16,430
Why did you put your hand in the fire?

587
01:07:16,508 --> 01:07:18,373
I never saw it before.

588
01:07:23,615 --> 01:07:25,139
No knowledge of fire.

589
01:07:27,152 --> 01:07:28,414
No books.

590
01:07:32,590 --> 01:07:34,114
I'm terribly sorry.

591
01:07:35,894 --> 01:07:39,295
I'm sorry I was angry with your people.
I had no right to be.

592
01:07:41,432 --> 01:07:45,664
No more than if I'd visited
the island of Bali in my own time.

593
01:07:50,775 --> 01:07:52,367
But, you know, Weena...

594
01:07:53,311 --> 01:07:57,839
You were safe inside your great house,
yet came out into the night to warn me.

595
01:07:58,650 --> 01:08:02,882
The characteristic which distinguished man
from the animal kingdom...

596
