...was the spirit of self-sacrifice.

597
01:08:07,559 --> 01:08:09,288
And you have that quality.

598
01:08:10,428 --> 01:08:14,660
I think all your people have it, really.
It just needs someone to reawaken it.

599
01:08:18,269 --> 01:08:19,793
I'd like to try if you'd let me.

600
01:08:20,738 --> 01:08:21,898
Will you?

601
01:08:23,074 --> 01:08:24,541
I do not understand...

602
01:08:26,211 --> 01:08:27,337
...but I believe you.

603
01:08:28,379 --> 01:08:30,472
That's as good a start as any.

604
01:08:33,451 --> 01:08:37,114
Try to tell me. The Morlocks.
Who or what are the Morlocks?

605
