of the past?

608
01:08:50,835 --> 01:08:52,427
There is no past.

609
01:08:55,840 --> 01:08:57,774
Do they ever wonder about the future?

610
01:08:59,811 --> 01:09:01,176
There is no future.

611
01:09:07,018 --> 01:09:08,417
The past...

612
