637
01:10:49,354 --> 01:10:50,343
What sort of rings?

638
01:10:50,988 --> 01:10:52,080
Rings that talk.

639
01:10:54,392 --> 01:10:56,690
Could you show me these talking rings?

640
01:11:07,138 --> 01:11:08,628
Come, this way!

641
01:11:23,688 --> 01:11:25,815
- These are the talking rings?
- Yes.

642
01:11:28,559 --> 01:11:29,526
They speak?

643
