<i>... rnade his own decision.</i>

662
01:12:42,467 --> 01:12:46,233
<i>Sorne chose to take refuge</i>
<i>in the great caverns...</i>

663
01:12:46,304 --> 01:12:50,240
<i>... and find a new way of life</i>
<i>far below the earth's surface.</i>

664
01:12:51,576 --> 01:12:55,569
<i>The rest of us decided</i>
<i>to take our chances in the sunlight...</i>

665
01:12:57,114 --> 01:13:00,015
<i>... srnall as those chances rnight be.</i>

666
01:13:01,452 --> 01:13:05,616
<i>Frorn the talking rings I learned</i>
<i>how the hurnan race divided itself...</i>

667
01:13:06,023 --> 01:13:09,550
<i>... and how the world of the Eloi</i>
<i>and the Morlocks began.</i>

668
01:13:11,028 --> 01:13:13,826
<i>By sorne awful quirk of fate...</i>

669
