Answer me!

682
01:15:00,838 --> 01:15:02,100
Where are you?

683
01:15:30,134 --> 01:15:31,533
What's happening?

684
01:15:33,037 --> 01:15:34,368
What's happening?

685
01:15:35,806 --> 01:15:37,797
What's the matter with you all?

686
01:15:55,893 --> 01:15:56,791
Weena, stop!

687
01:16:46,811 --> 01:16:47,607
Stop!

688
01:16:49,947 --> 01:16:51,471
What happens to them?

689
01:16:55,553 --> 01:16:59,319
Don't stand there like fattened cattle!
Will you answer me?

690
01:17:01,692 --> 01:17:03,125
What is wrong?

691
01:17:03,861 --> 01:17:06,227
There is nothing wrong. It is all clear.

692
01:17:09,366 --> 01:17:10,958
What do you mean, "All clear"?

693
01:17:11,268 --> 01:17:12,633
All clear.

694
01:17:15,005 --> 01:17:18,406
In the middle of the 1900s,
the falling bombs, the people calling out:

695
01:17:18,476 --> 01:17:19,636
