722
01:24:20,030 --> 01:24:22,624
Get up the stairs!
That's the way out! Quickly!

723
01:25:30,167 --> 01:25:32,032
The torch!

724
01:25:37,040 --> 01:25:38,166
Get the torch!

725
01:26:31,528 --> 01:26:33,928
Get up the stairs! Hurry up!

726
