That's fine.

728
01:28:23,306 --> 01:28:24,933
Come on, throw it down!

729
01:28:26,777 --> 01:28:28,176
All the dead wood!

730
01:28:32,015 --> 01:28:33,141
Throw it down!

731
01:28:33,216 --> 01:28:35,207
Do the same to the other wells!

732
01:28:35,685 --> 01:28:37,550
